You focus on the intricacies of the magic binding you to your eidolon to extend the duration of your [[Boost Eidolon]] or [[Reinforce Eidolon]] spell. 

If your next action is to cast [[Boost Eidolon]] or [[Reinforce Eidolon]], attempt a skill check with the skill associated with the tradition of magic you gain from your eidolon (such as Nature for a primal eidolon). The DC is usually a standard-difficulty DC of your level, but the GM can assign a different DC based on the circumstances. 

